description: This Chainlink VRF common Gatinho purrs with a rating of 35, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 70, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and Box for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50352-51442-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [70 Votes, Common]
